(90, 1, '2019-10-26 21:17:59', '2019-10-26 20:17:59', '<!-- Default form contact -->\nHere at SQUARE, we care for our environment. This is why we encourage employees to submit sustainability challenges for their co-workers. Climate challenges can have many faces such as planting trees and collecting trash in natural reserve areas. Thereby we hope to counter-act climate change, increase awareness among our employees and build a sense of social community and responsibility for the climate.\n\n<form class=\"text-center border border-light p-5\" action=\"#!\">\n<p class=\"h4 mb-4\"></p>\n<label>How can we contact you?</label>\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"defaultContactFormName\" class=\"form-control mb-4\" placeholder=\"Name\">\n\n<!-- Email -->\n<input type=\"email\" id=\"defaultContactFormEmail\" class=\"form-control mb-4\" placeholder=\"E-mail\">\n\n<!-- Subject -->\n<p class=\"h4 mb-4\">What is your idea?</p>\n<select class=\"browser-default custom-select mb-4\">\n<option value=\"\" disabled=\"\">Categorise your idea</option>\n<option value=\"1\" selected=\"\">Corporate event</option>\n<option value=\"2\">Employee event</option>\n<option value=\"3\">Behaviour change</option>\n<option value=\"4\">Policy change</option>\n</select>\n\n<!-- Message -->\n<div class=\"form-group\">\n        <textarea class=\"form-control rounded-0\" id=\"exampleFormControlTextarea2\" rows=\"3\" placeholder=\"Please describe your idea briefly and we\'ll get back to you as soon as possible. Thanks for participating in making our company better every day!\"></textarea></div>\n<!-- Send button -->\n<button class=\"btn btn-info btn-block\" type=\"submit\">Send</button>\n\n</form><!-- Default form contact -->', 'Submit a sustainability challenge', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'submit-challenge', '', '', '2019-10-29 10:35:56', '2019-10-29 10:35:56', '', 0, 'https://www.climactiv.de/?page_id=90', 0, 'page', '', 0),
